snippet.title: Rivals 2 - Maypul Moveset Breakdown
snippet.description:
Maypul joins the cast in Rivals 2 as the latest character in our 2024 launch roster! Revealed live on the #evo2023 main stage, here is a deep dive into her moveset narrated by our Community Manager, George Rogers. Learn more and show your support for the game at https://rivals2.com/wishlist 
Music by RESOFORCE: https://resoforce.bandcamp.com/album/rivals-of-aether-resonant-mixes
#rivalsofaether  #rivals2  #indiegame
